dct_title_s: Index to administrative units for Shimonoseki and Moji. A.M.S. L902
dct_description_sm: A"Cautiion this map for use only as administrative listing reference." "Administrative names and locations are correct to November 1943." This is an index for map on verso: Shimonoseki and Moji, Honshu and Kyushu, Japan. It is filed under call number for map on verso: G7964.S44C2.1945.A7M3.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1945.
